{"tid":413093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒手足試過在街拿派的衛生巾用","createTime":"2017-09-25T08:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T13:50:06.000Z","uid":70205,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7159698993766593625aa5133c01553b362eeef5","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:28:34.000Z","msg":"我逛街時常看見有人派衛生巾與女士,我雖然是位男士,但我都好想拿取她們所派的衛生巾,因為我都好想知道它是怎樣的.所以我一股勇氣之下向那個派衛生巾的人員伸手拿取一片衛生巾了.回家後我立刻把衛生巾的包裝紙撕去,然後臭一臭衛生巾的氣味是怎樣,但發覺沒有甚麼特別.再清楚一點,發覺它背面像一張貼紙用作貼著內褲.我將它貼在內褲內然後穿回內褲發覺很舒服很柔軟,忽然我的小弟撥起了.之後我忍不了打飛機,最後我射落衛生巾的吸水部份.它內裡的吸水珠珠果然勵害,立刻把精液吸收.突然我聽到家裡大門的鎖匙聲,我立刻把衛生巾拋落街.我從這件事得到了一個答案,就是衛生巾的威力好勁,而有月事需要貼衛生巾的女士個西一定舒服."},{"pid":"5ed7b33c06a6e761229a4b5cbd27758a7a3a89b0","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"沒人試過嗎？"},{"pid":"e23156bdc62e7ca55fb5e1fe406d3be1a4dfb60d","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f62bc32f43473d3ace10735e5d541aa7f4be21f","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"很多負皮"},{"pid":"4755d45ee391e7190f07fe07819341a15836f0cb","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bdf6167031fa53d038712411c6c9d2d8939aec","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4e4c45ed18102f6caf01b1862944feccaf8792","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a294dd2f938d7d1fa13258e460a3466704ac88d5","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cd859ff14460586c70e6fe6134a9253bb30f76","tid":413093,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"係咪思覺老師d文黎?"},{"pid":"19615239683bf27554067a6778b253293ddba0ad","tid":413093,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a62fd3f971789629704206503264ec8ff09ad209","tid":413093,"uid":70205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無啦啦痴左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}